SUBJECT: AMERICAN PEOPLE SHOULD BE INFORMED OF THE TRUTH     FILE: UFO2567




Dear Senator,

We, the undersigned, believe that on July 2, 1947 "something" crashed
about 75 miles northwest of Roswell, New Mexico on a ranch near Corona,
New Mexico. We further believe that the American Military and intelli-
ence communities cover up the truth about this incident for reasons
known only to those involved in the cover-up.

We, the undersigned, believe the time has come for the American People
to be informed of the truth behind this incident and the cover-up to end.
It is for this purpose that we have affixed our names and signatures to
this petition demanding that your office create a committee to review
the facts, the testimony of the eyewitnesses, and determine once and for
all, the truth and validity of this incident.

It is in the spirit of Government by the People, for the People and of
the People that this petition is presented.

